Writing Exercise 2:

Client:Hello!Are you there?

Freelancer:Hi.Yes,I am available.I wanted to check in on the projects project's
progress and see if you have any specific updates or new requirements.

Client:Hello!The initial designs you submitted were great,and team loved them.

Freelancer:It's my pleasure that you liked the designs!I'm more than happy to make those adjustments for you.
Just let me know the details,and I'll get right on it.

Client:Perfect!Could you provide us with a few more layout options for the homepage?

Freelancer:Obviously,recently I'll start working with those.You can see the updated versions by tomorrow in
the evening.

Client:That sounds great.We have a tight deadline for this project,so your promptness is much appreciated.

Freelancer:I can understand the importance of deadlines.If there anything else you need then I am always with 
you.

Client:Thank you for your dedication!

Freelancer:I'm always prepared to take any new challenges and assist with your future projects.

Client:That's good.We'll definitely keep in touch.

Freelancer:Well,I'll get to work now and keep you updated on the progress.Have a nice day!	